#each flow contains pareto 
#distributed number of packets.
#- PEarrival
#flow arrival is poissson and 
#each flow contains pareto 
#distributed number of packets.
#- PBarrival
#flow arrival is poissson and 
#each flow contains bimodal
#distributed number of packets.

#Variables:#
